f=Product/ux/custom/study-design/SKILL.md · in=study run findings trustworthy: protocol written before recruiting, consent handled, sample matched question, leading questions designed out. Rigor front what separates evidence anecdote. · p=study leading script convenience sample produces confident garbage poisons repository. Designing protocol before running matching method question research earns right cited. · wu=research-repository returns GAP real unknown worth new study)., PRD assumption needs primary evidence none exists., loom needs qualitative input experiment moved (or didn't). · st:/ Protocol=QUESTION (one precise research question "do users understand pricing page" "is product good") METHOD MATCH (the question picks method: generative interviews/JTBD; evaluative usability test; magnitude survey; behavioral funnel, metric's turf) PROTOCOL (script written before recruiting; leading/loaded questions designed out; tasks opinions behavior question) SAMPLE (size recruit criteria matched claim's needed confidence; `<FILL_IN: usability suggested ~5/round reasoning-based until research-methods source>`; convenience samples labeled such) CONSENT (recorded, data-handling stated; sensitive data minimized Fleet Charter least-privilege, research edition) RUN hand raw data synthesis-discipline. · in=One question study study asking five things answers none well; extra questions extra studies. Method follows question, habit: don't survey learn *why* (interviews) interview learn *how many* (survey). Mismatched method design failure caught here, synthesis. Design out leading questions script reviewed questions suggest their answer; biased instrument can't un-biased analysis. Sample matches claim: generalizable claim needs representative sample; directional signal say fewer. sample's limits stated front ride finding's confidence. Consent minimization non-negotiable: recorded consent, stated data handling, least sensitive data answers question (Fleet Charter Rail spirit). · of=Study plan: question method (with match rationale) protocol/script sample (size, criteria, limits) consent plan. Raw data synthesis-discipline. · pr=Protocol before recruiting; question before method., Design bias out you can't analyze out., Sample matches claim; limits stated, hidden. · f=Can't recruit ideal sample? Run available one, label limits explicitly, cap finding's confidence accordingly (honest-thinness, fake rigor). · b:with Other Skills=research-repository gates entry (only GAPs get studies) receives findings; synthesis-discipline turns raw data confidence-flagged claims., metric owns behavioral/quant magnitude funnel; owns qualitative *why* co-cited study spans both., usability-testing jtbd-interviews (marketplace candidates, searched 2026-07-10, queued scout) deepen specific methods; method rigor custom regardless.